Consider that wc3lib will support runtime linking/loading which means that libraries
are being loaded at runtime and if this fails an exception is being thrown.

Flags:
EDITOR - Qt/KDE 4 are required!

cmake options:
BUILD_DOCUMENTATION - Generates doxygen documentation (doxygen is required)

DEPRACATED:
Compilation flags for native format conversion support:
BLP:
	- JPEG
	- PNG
	- TGA

MDLX:
	- BLEND
	- MAX

MPQ:
	- TAR

EDITOR

cmake options:
BUILD_DOCUMENTATION